imple, safe and secure for retail and business customers. Coincover is growing fast. Since our initial launch in June we are already covering more than 10,000 wallets, protecting more than $250Million in crypto assets, have helped recover $300K+ funds. Yet, this is just the beginning and this is a brilliant opportunity to get in on a start-up right at the beginning. Cryptocurrency ownership is growing fast and getting more mainstream but to many it still feels like a risky investment. Coincover is changing this. Backed by Hambro Perks Insurtech Gateway, the Development Bank of Wales and others, we are creating the easiest way to protect and manage digital currency anywhere in the world. Apply Please send your CV along with a message as to why your are interested in the role to careers@coincover.com CompanyOur CompanyBlogHelpCareersContact Us LegalTerms &Â ConditionsPrivacy PolicyModern Slavery StatementCookie PolicyCancellation &Â Refund Policy Sign up to our newsletter to hear about our latest news and products. Thank you! Your submission has been received! Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form. Digital Asset Services Ltd (trading as Coincover) is registered in England and Wales under company number 11356137 and its registered office is at Capital Building, Tyndall Street, Cardiff, CF10 4AZ. Coincover is registered with the Financial Conduct Authority."
